Subject: Flash Comics!
Description: No we're not talking about the fastest man alive, we're talking about the wild new form of comics that incorporate the technology of today! These comics keep you on the edge of your seat and pull you in even deeper with stunning animations interwoven into the frames! Just when you thought you knew comics!  Speakers include:Kayla Nelson, BluRaven C. Houvener, Jon David - Track: Comics  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
